## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of APRNs' roles in promoting nursing-based outcome studies. Additionally, the findings are limited to the context of the sources reviewed and may not reflect the full scope of practices in different healthcare settings. Further research and direct input from practicing APRNs could provide a more comprehensive understanding.